metadata.name: alien jizz
metadata.description:
i utilized a sound-sketch i made with a roland mc-505 to trigger the values of different force fields in C4D

those forcefields than have been used to direct particle-simulations to generate meshes via volume builders and path-tracers



digital sculpture built and renedred in C4D processed in photoshop

8000p x 4500p 300dpi
